dct_title_s: Australian mineral exploration review 2018-19 / compiled by Anthony Senior ; cartography by Silvio Mezzomo.
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading, depth shown by isolines. eCat No. 133031. Also available online from the website of Geoscience Australia at: www.ga.gov.au (Viewed 8 September 2020) Includes text, four graphs, Australian critical minerals map, and legends. Australian Mineral Exploration Review 2018-19 map is on the reverse side. "January 2020"
